124
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:47,760
War

125
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:48,680
or peace.

126
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,240
Each has pros and cons.

127
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,960
It's a matter of whether it benefits

128
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,720
Daqing or serves your own interests.

129
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,920
Boss.

130
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:47,040
Any more wontons?

131
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,480
Mr. Wen Junior,

132
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,200
