153
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,920
and eager to learn.

154
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,080
Your future's looking bright.

155
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,040
I have the Wen family to thank for that.

156
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,120
I saw a lot,

157
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,320
learned a lot,

158
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,480
and understood a lot.

159
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,440
Otherwise,

160
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,160
I'd still be the old Chen Pan'er,

161
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,560
